item.title: CVE-2020-6297|2024-08-04T08:55:22.435Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20data%20intelligence
item.description: Under certain conditions the upgrade of SAP Data Hub 2.7 to SAP Data Intelligence, version - 3.0, allows an attacker to access confidential system configuration information, that should otherwise be restricted, leading to Information Disclosure.
